    \tr{\td{Sensor module ×8}\td{D1/D2 top source/detector}\td{Current clear top photo plus optical/electrical evidence}\td{No current-fill image in the saved packet; use optical/electrical evidence before any diode claim}\td{Verify optically/electrically; not a purchase task unless bench evidence contradicts the board}\td{Record evidence; do not create a parts order from images alone}}
